<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094251>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Xenorthrius umbratus: Lower surface of head and pronotum with mouthparts." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094251/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094253>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Gular process: (A) Xenorthrius penangis and (B) Xenorthrius umbratus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094253/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094255>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Antennae: (A) Xenorthrius doliaris, (B) Xenorthrius abruptepunctatus, (C) Xenorthrius simplex and (D) Xenorthrius berndi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094255/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094257>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Pronota: (A) Xenorthrius truncatus, (B) Xenorthrius ephippiatus and (C) Xenorthrius decoratus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094257/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094259>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Elytral apices: (A) dentate (Xenorthrius truncatus), (B) dehiscent (Xenorthrius prolongatus) and (C) rounded (Xenorthrius geniculatus)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094259/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094261>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Xenorthrius scordalus: rasp-like punctation in basal half of elytra." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094261/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10094263>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Xenorthrius loricus: Wing venation. AA = anal anterior, CuA = cubitus anterior, MP = media posterior, Rc = radial cell, Sc = subcosta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10094263/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

